RealActuatorData - Annotation Type in fr.upmc.dtgui.annotations
The annotation RealActuatorData tags setter methods of a robot with information concerning how to use the corresponding real data in the robot representation as a control over the robot's behavior.
RealRange - Annotation Type in fr.upmc.dtgui.annotations
The annotation RealRange is used in an annotation RealSensorData ou RealActuatorData to define the range of admissible values for the corresponding data.
RealSensorData - Annotation Type in fr.upmc.dtgui.annotations
The annotation RealSensorData tags getter methods of a robot with information concerning how to use the corresponding real data in the robot representation as a property that can be observed to look into the robot's state.
